msgid "Showfoto"
msgstr "Showfoto"

#. (itstool) path: component/summary
#: org.kde.showfoto.appdata.xml:7
msgid "Image Editor"
msgstr "ຕົວແກ້ໄຂຮູບພາບ"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.showfoto.appdata.xml:9
msgid ""
"Showfoto is a fast Image Editor with powerful image editing tools. You can "
"use it to view your photographs and improve them. Showfoto is the standalone "
"image editor of the digiKam project."
msgstr "Showfoto ເປັນໂປຣແກຣມແກ້ໄຂຮູບພາບທີ່ວ່ອງໄວ ພ້ອມດ້ວຍເຄື່ອງມືແກ້ໄຂຮູບພາບທີ່ມີປະສິດທິພາບ. ທ່ານສາມາດໃຊ້ມັນເພື່ອເບິ່ງຮູບພາບ ແລະ ປັບປຸງພວກມັນໃຫ້ດີຂຶ້ນ. Showfoto ແມ່ນຕົວແກ້ໄຂຮູບພາບແບບແຍກດ່ຽວຂອງໂຄງການ digiKam."

#. (itstool) path: screenshot/caption
#: org.kde.showfoto.appdata.xml:20
msgid "Editing photo in Showfoto"
msgstr "ການແກ້ໄຂຮູບພາບໃນ Showfoto"

